item.title: 【Requests】[REQ AUD] - Mariah Carey's 'Vision of Love' Single FLAC Files - Seeking 'Prisoner / All in Your Mind / Someday' Excerpts
item.description:
Is anyone in possession of the FLAC files for Mariah Carey's 'Vision of Love' single? I'm particularly interested in special excerpts from the debut release 'Prisoner / All in Your Mind / Someday.' If anyone has access to these files and is willing to share or rip them, I would greatly appreciate it.

Thank you!
